description:
Ballistic High-Speed pushes the frontier of how we view and understand the vast world of firearms, ballistics, explosives, and many other topics by examining high-energy, high-velocity events with world class imaging.

Bryce Fritzel, a High-Speed Imaging Technician of a decade, specializes in using Phantom cameras to analyze anything that is too fast to see, but too important not to.

Adam Knowles, our Armorer and Weapons Specialist, is dedicated to pushing the boundaries of our industry through research and acquisition of the tools and hardware to answer the most important questions.

description:
"Do or Die" is a English idiomatic expression that means:

- A situation where someone must succeed or face severe consequences
- A critical moment where failure is not an option
- A situation where one must give their best effort to achieve something

In Hindi, the phrase "Do or Die" can be translated to:

- "करो या मरो" (Karo ya Maro)
- "जीतो या हारो" (Jito ya Haro)
- "सफल होना ही है" (Safal Hona Hi Hai)

The phrase is often used in situations where someone is faced with a significant challenge or a high-stakes decision, and they must muster all their strength and resources to succeed.

Beijing Institute of Mathematical Sciences and Applications is a world-class new research institution jointly built with Tsinghua University. BIMSA aims to promote the development of mathematical science, foster cross-disciplinary integration of mathematics with other sciences, cultivate and expand the talent base engaged in mathematical research in China, attract scientists and researchers globally, and establish an international academic exchange platform. 
The 2024 International Congress of Basic Science will be held from July 14 to July 26. This annual event will bring together leading experts from all around to celebrate basic sciences –Mathematics, Theoretical Physics and Theoretical Computer and Information Science. Subsequent event and lectures will mainly take place at BIMSA. Over 1000 participants, including some 400 distinguished scholars, 5 Fields Medalists and 3 Turing Medal winners, 1 Nobel laureate, and numerous academicians are expected to attend.

My dear Friends 🥰All of you are heartily welcome to your own channel nigamrailwaychannel
Friends, if you have to go somewhere far, everyone's favourite way to travel is by train because trains have facilities for everything 🙂
Friends, what should you keep in mind while travelling by train? Do not board or get off a moving train. Travel in a safe place in the train coach, do not make too many friends with strangers and do not eat anyone's food, do not travel standing at the door, while charging your mobile in the window, the window must be tied up.
In case of luggage theft in a train, you should immediately contact the train conductor, coach attendant, guard or GRP escort. They will give you an FIR form, which you have to fill and submit to them. After this, your complaint will be sent to the police station for necessary action.
If your mobile is stolen in a train, immediately contact RPF and register your complaint.
Travel by train carefully my brother and please support me 🙏

description:
My channel is a collection of golf swing videos of professional golfers. Most of the videos have been taken with the Casio Exilim EX-FH25 or Sony RX10  IV / RX100 VI cameras (at either 240 or 250 frames-per-second). Normally the videos are taken at a shutter speed of around 1/2500  to give sharpness to the club and hands during the downswing. If better equipment is available I will try it out!

Most of the videos have been taken at European Tour events – mostly UK events - though sometimes I venture out as far as Denmark, Turkey and most recently Australia. All the videos are taken during practice days or pro-ams and are never taken during the tournament days.

Enjoy the videos!

Michael Field

description:
Das Institut für Bauweisen und Strukturtechnologie gehört zum Deutschen Zentrum für Luft- und Raumfahrt (DLR) und entwickelt Hochleistungsstrukturen für viele Anwendungsbereiche (Luft- und Raumfahrt, Verkehr u.a.) von der Konzeption bis zur Produktionstechnologie.
Das Institut verteilt sich auf die zwei Standorte Stuttgart und Augsburg.

In Stuttgart sind vier Abteilungen angesiedelt:
- Bauteilgestaltung und Fertigungstechnologien
- Keramische Verbundstrukturen
- Strukturelle Integrität
- Raumfahrt Systemintegration

In Augsburg befindet sich die Abteilung „Automatisierung und Qualitätssicherung in der Produktion“.
Diese Abteilung ist gleichzeitig das DLR „Zentrum für Leichtbauproduktionstechnologie“ (ZLP) am Standort Augsburg.

I’m Faran Afzal, a passionate traveller and social media influencer with a community of 71k followers on Instagram, 65k subscribers on YouTube, and 35k followers on Facebook. My story began in the small town of Daltonganj, Jharkhand, with nothing but dreams and a Suzuki Max 100.

工研院(ITRI)成立於1973年，以「創新、誠信、分享」的核心價值，持續深耕前瞻性、關鍵性的技術，為了人類更美好的未來而努力，關懷日漸老化的人口，預見未來環境的趨勢，回應對智慧化的需求；並聚焦於綠能環境、健康照護、智慧生活等跨領域整合，以創新科技的研發，謀求人類社會福祉，為產業社會帶來更美好的未來。 

The Industrial Technology Research Institute (ITRI) is a nonprofit R&D organization engaged in applied research and technical services. Founded in 1973, ITRI has played a vital role in transforming Taiwan’s economy from a labor-intensive industry to a high-tech industry. Numerous well-known, high-tech companies in Taiwan, such as leaders in the semiconductor industry TSMC and UMC, can trace their origins to ITRI.

description: Welcome to Tattoo Lovers - your ultimate destination for all things tattoos! Join our community of fellow tattoo lovers from around the world and stay up-to-date on the latest in the tattoo industry. Don't forget to hit that subscribe button and turn on notifications to never miss a new video!
